Installment payments
NordVPN offers an option where its users can split their payment for NordVPN’s 3-year plan into three monthly installments instead of paying all at once when signing up. Please note that we apply a nominal interest rate of 17% to the total amount of any Services purchased using an installment payment option. If you choose to pay in installments, your initial payment will occur on the date of purchase. Subsequent payments will be made 30 and 60 days after the purchase date. If the full price is not evenly divisible by 3, your final payment amount will be smaller.

