Users that purchased NordVPN with installment payments are eligible for a refund within 30 days of their initial payment only. All other terms of our refund policy remain applicable.

By choosing to pay in installments, you agree to maintain linked to your NordVPN account at least one valid credit card that expires no earlier than 20 days after your last payment due date. If we are unable to charge you for any subsequent payments, we will make 3 subsequent attempts to charge the same card. If we still fail to receive any subsequent payments, we will cease providing our Services to you after a given time, depending on which payment failed to reach us: i) if we did not receive the first payment after the initial payment, your funds will be used to render service for 90 days from the date of the purchase; ii) if we did not receive the second payment after the initial payment, your funds will be used to render service for 1 year from the date of the purchase.

